2. Use utility classes efficiently. For complex class logic, use `clsx` or `tailwind-merge`.
3. If I ask for UI components, prioritize using Shadcn/UI patterns if applicable (Radix UI primitives).
4. Ensure responsive design (mobile-first approach) in all UI snippets.

